Sylvie Florence Mballa Éloundou (amụrụ na 21 Eprel, na afọ 1977) bụ onye na-agba ọsọ French-Cameroonian nke na-ahụ maka 100 mita.
Nwa amaala Yaoundé, isi obodo Cameroon, Sylvie Mballa Éloundou nọchitere anya mba a mụrụ ya, mana ọ gbanwere mba na 10 Ọktoba, na afọ 2002 iji sọọ mpi dị ka onye otu ndị France
Mgbe mgbanwe ọzọ gasịrị, na 1 Eprel, na afọ 2005, ọ banyere ọzọ na asọmpi n'okpuru ọkọlọtọ Cameroon.

Oge kachasị mma ya maka mita 100 bụ 11.13 sekọnd, nke o nwetara na onwa Julaị, na afọ 2005 na Angers, Otú ọ dị, na afọ 2006 IAAF World Indoor Championships na Moscow, ọ gwụchara ọsọ mita 60 n'ọnọdụ nke asatọ.
